I have official documents of my company in Vietnam. Can this be used for verification?

Newsbreak is a US-only traffic source, and for business verification, we typically require documents that are relevant to the US. If you have any specific questions or need further assistance, please email adsupport@newsbreak.com with your query.
May I ask if your team also works on Saturdays? I had already sent an email on Saturday.

Our team typically reviews ads within 4 hours on weekdays and up to 8 hours on weekends, including Saturdays. If you sent an email on Saturday, it should be reviewed within that timeframe. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
